Class ProviderRecord

java.lang.Object
chocAnSystem.RosterRecord
chocAnSystem.ProviderRecord
public class ProviderRecord extends RosterRecord
This class is a record of every Provider in the ChocAn system. Each contact has the provider's name, number, address, cite, state, zip, and account fee..
Version:
1.0
Author:
Emily Steinbach
